nt%20officers%20(the%20UCs)%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20them%20he%20wanted%20them%20to%20steal%20documents%2C%20arrange%20protests%20at%20political%20rallies%2C%20and%20kill%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20person%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plot%20would%20have%20to%20be%20carried%20out%20after%20he%20left%20the%20country%2C%20and%20they%20would%20be%20told%20who%20the%20target%20was%20either%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20August%20or%20the%20first%20week%20of%20September%2C%20Merchant%20told%20the%20undercover%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerchant%20arranged%20to%20pay%20USD%205%2C000%20in%20cash%20as%20an%20advance%20for%20the%20assassination%20services%20and%20successfully%20delivered%20this%20payment%20on%20June%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%20transaction%2C%20he%20made%20plans%20to%20leave%20the%20country%20on%20July%2012%2C%202024%2C%20one%20day%20before%20Donald%20Trump's%20assassination%20attempt.%20However%2C%20law%20enforcement%20intervened%20and%20arrested%20him%20before%20he%20could%20leave%2C%20the%20court%20document%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723007940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Furc6du9_asif-merchant_625x300_07_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fasif-merchant-who-is-asif-merchant-man-arrested-for-plot-to-kill-donald-trump-6281531%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20has%20charged%20a%20Pakistani%20man%2C%20who%20allegedly%20has%20ties%20to%20Iran%2C%20with%20attempting%20to%20carry%20out%20assassinations%20of%20American%20politicians.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fasif-merchant-who-is-asif-merchant-man-arrested-for-plot-to-kill-donald-trump-6281531%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fasif-merchant-who-is-asif-merchant-man-arrested-for-plot-to-kill-donald-t