2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20court%20documents%2C%20others%20may%20also%20have%20been%20intended%20victims%20because%20of%20the%20mention%20of%20targets%20in%20the%20plural.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFederal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation(FBI)%20Chief%20Christopher%20Wray%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20dangerous%20murder-for-hire%20plot%20exposed%20in%20today's%20charges%20allegedly%20was%20orchestrated%20by%20a%20Pakistani%20national%20with%20close%20ties%20to%20Iran%20and%20is%20straight%20out%20of%20the%20Iranian%20playbook.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20plotter%2C%20who%20is%20also%20known%20as%20Asif%20Raza%20Merchant%2C%20told%20officials%20that%20he%20has%20two%20wives%2C%20one%20each%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20in%20Iran%2C%20as%20well%20as%20children%20in%20both%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20complaint%20filed%20in%20the%20Federal%20court%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20the%20plot%20reads%20like%20a%20spy%20thriller%20with%20an%20elaborate%20scheme%20to%20burglarise%20the%20home%20of%20a%20target%2C%20creating%20diversions%20with%20protests%20and%20rallies%2C%20and%20killing%20the%20politician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20included%20a%20show%20of%20bonding%20between%20Merchant%2C%2046%2C%20and%20the%20undercover%20officers%20he%20thought%20were%20professional%20killers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20papers%20said%20the%20plot%20involved%20multiple%20elements%3A%20stealing%20documents%20or%20USB%20drives%20from%20a%20target's%20home%3B%20planning%20protests%2C%20and%20killing%20a%20politician%20or%20government%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerchant%20made%20up%20code%20names%20for%20each%20element%20in%20the%20plot%3A%20%26quot%3Btee-shirt%26quot%3B%20for%20protests%2C%20%26quot%3Bflannel%20shirt%26quot%3B%20for%20stealing%20documents%2C%20%26quot%3Bfleece%20jacket%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20assassination%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Byarn-dye%26quot%3B%20for%20their%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20entice%20the%20person%20he%20contacted%20first%20and%20who%20informed%20officials%2C%20Merchant%20told%20him%20that%20he%20has%20an%20uncle%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Byarn-dyed%26quot%3B%20business%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20he%20could%20go%20into%20business%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20the%20government%20source%20he%20thought%20was%20an%20assassin%20for%20hire%20to%20explain%20how%20the%20target%20would%20die%20in%20different%20scenarios.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revelation%20about%20this%20plot%20comes%20less%20than%20a%20month%20after%20the%20July%2013%20failed%20assassination%20attempt%20on%20Trump%20in%20Butler%2C%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20a%20connection%20between%20the%20plot%20by%20Merchant%20and%20that%20attempt%2C%20which%20officials%20have%20said%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20a%20lone%20wolf%2C%20a%20person%20unconnected%20to%20any%20group%20or%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plot%20failed%20because%20Merchant%20tried%20to%20recruit%20FBI%20agents%20for%20the%20assassination%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFortunately%2C%20the%20assassins%20Merchant%20tried%20to%20hire%20were%20undercover%20FBI%20agents%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Christie%20Curtis%2C%20the%20Acting%20Assistant%20Director%20of%20the%20New%20York%20FBI%20Field%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20arrested%20on%20July%2012%20as%20he%20was%20getting%20ready%20to%20catch%20a%20flight%20out%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerchant%20arrived%20in%20the%20US%20in%20April%20from%20Pakistan%20after%20spending%20time%20in%20Iran%2C%20according%20to%20the%20version%20of%20the%20plot%20in%20court%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20contacted%20a%20person%20he%20thought%20could%20help%20him%20and%20that%20person%20reported%20it%20to%20law%20enforcement%20and%20became%20a%20confidential%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-June%2C%20Merchant%20met%20with%20people%20he%20thought%20were%20hitmen%2C%20but%20were%20undercover%20US%20law%20enforcement%20officers%20(the%20UCs)%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20them%20he%20wanted%20them%20to%20steal%20documents%2C%20arrange%20protests%20at%20political%20rallies%2C%20and%20kill%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20person%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plot%20would%20have%20to%20be%20carried%20out%20after%20he%20left%20the%20country%20and%20in%20either%20the%20last%20week%20of%20August%20or%20the%20first%20week%20of%20September%20they%20would%20be%20told%20who%20the%20target%20was%2C%20Merchant%20told%20the%20undercover%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20received%20%245%2C000%20from%20overseas%20and%20made%20a%20down%20payment%20to%20the%20undercover%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20court%20papers%2C%20one%20of%20the%20agents%20said%20after%20getting%20the%20money%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%20we%20know%20we're%20going%20forward.%20We're%20doing%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20which%20Merchant%20responded%3A%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20absolutely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20violence%20is%20a%20constant%20worry%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20a%20man%20was%20arrested%20in%20Virginia%20for%20allegedly%20threatening%20to%20kill%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20presidential%20nominee%20Kamala%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKamala%20Harris%20needs%20to%20be%20put%20on%20fire%20alive.%20I%20will%20do%20it%20personally%20if%20no%20one%20else%20does...%20I%20want%20her%20to%20suffer%20a%20slow%20agonising%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20Frank%20Lucio%20Carillo%20posted%20on%20a%20right-wing%20social%20media%20site%2C%20according%20to%20the%20FBI%20complaint%20in%20a%20Federal%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20allegedly%20threatened%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20FBI%20Chief%20Wray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723007040000%2C%22visua