0will%20be%20amazing%20irrespective%20of%20which%20home%20you%20eat%20it%20in.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20taste%20profiles%20also%20change%20across%20generations.%20Farida%20agrees.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%20cooking%20I%20used%20to%20stay%20exactly%20true%20to%20my%20great-grandmother%E2%80%99s%20and%20mother%E2%80%99s%20recipes.%20But%20now%20I%20allow%20myself%20a%20little%20variation%2C%20a%20little%20additions%20here%20and%20there%20and%20a%20change%20in%20technique.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20example%20is%20the%20strawberry%20jam%20and%20custard%20cake%20in%20which%20Farida%20has%20deviated%20slightly%20from%20the%20original%20recipe%20and%20added%20a%20substitute%20for%20the%20usual%20milk.%20Another%20example%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Esalli%20%3C%2Fem%3Echicken%20where%20she%20has%20added%20a%20few%20more%20ingredients%20and%20changed%20the%20technique%20of%20cooking%20the%20onions%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Emasala%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffood-3-1722423057.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pomfret%20curry%20(L)%20and%20veg%20cheese%20bakedish%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffood-3-1722423057.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffood-3-1722423057-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffood-3-1722423057-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffood-3-1722423057-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffood-3-1722423057-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359205%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPomfret%20curry%20(L)%20and%20Veg%20cheese%20bakedish%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Farida%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20challenging%20to%20change%20recipes%20that%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F308289%2Ffood-writers-compile-a-kitchen-of-ones-own-book-to-document-heirloom-family-indian-recipes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproducts%20of%20heritage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20woes%20the%20recipes%20that%20have%20been%20lost%20simply%20because%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20written%20down.%20One%20of%20these%20is%20%3Cem%3Ekhattu%20gosht%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20spicy%20and%20sour%20mutton%20gravy).%20%E2%80%9CNone%20of%20us%20have%20the%20recipe.%20I%20grew%20up%20eating%20it%20on%20Sundays%20and%20auspicious%20days%2C%20but%20now%20the%20women%20in%20my%20family%20do%20not%20correctly%20recollect%20the%20exact%20set%20of%20ingredients%20and%20hand-pounded%20%3Cem%3Emasalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20went%20into%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Farida%20credits%20the%20matriarchs%20of%20the%20family%20for%20teaching%20her%20about%20cooking%2C%20she%20says%20she%20also%20learnt%20another%20important%20lesson%20from%20them.%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20do%20anything%20half-heartedly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20matter%20what%20time%20it%20is%2C%20if%20I%E2%80%99m%20making%20an%20order%20and%20I%20realise%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20short%20of%20even%20one%20ingredient%2C%20I%20will%20run%20to%20the%20store%20and%20get%20it.%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20deem%20a%20dish%20finished%20until%20I%20am%20satisfied%20that%20its%20taste%20matches%20the%20original%20version%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20order%20your%20feast%20at%208879132817%20or%207506192017.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E