al%20did%20for%20badminton%20in%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CLike%20table%20tennis%2C%20badminton%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20so%20famous%20(in%20India)%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Folympics.com%2Fen%2Fathletes%2Fmanika-batra%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManika%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20amount%20of%20recognition%20they%20have%20got%20for%20the%20sport%2C%20I%20would%20also%20like%20to%20take%20table%20tennis%20to%20greater%20heights%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhilst%20table%20tennis%20was%20her%20first%20love%2C%20Manika%20turned%20down%20modelling%20offers%20in%20her%20teens%20to%20concentrate%20on%20the%20sport.%20Her%20dedication%20has%20not%20only%20brought%20her%20personal%20success%20but%20has%20also%20inspired%20a%20generation%20of%20young%20table%20tennis%20players%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20laurels%20indeed%20make%20her%20a%20true%20icon%20of%20Indian%20table%20tennis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722849309000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359739%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Khel%20Ratna%20awardee%20Manika%20Batra%20has%20become%20a%20household%20name%20after%20her%20performance%20at%20Paris%20Olympics.%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20the%20table%20tennis%20player's%2015-year-long%20career.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LinkedIn%20For%20Blue%20Collar%20Jobs%3A%20Bihar%20Man%20Built%20India%E2%80%99s%201st%20Job%20Portal%20for%20Daily%20Wage%20Workers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJanuary%202020%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20rainy%20day%20in%20Delhi.%20Chandrashekar%20Mandal%20had%20just%20started%20work%20at%20his%20new%20finance%20job%20and%20was%20enjoying%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%