neur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWatching%20this%20might%20have%20been%20very%20tough%20for%20many%2C%20but%20it%20was%20a%20lived%20reality%20for%20millions%20like%20Sumit%20Kumar%2C%20a%20construction%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Gopalganj%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Sumit%20had%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20for%20work.%20He%20walked%20for%20two%20days%20before%20hitching%20rides%20on%20buses%20and%20trucks%20to%20reach%20home%2C%20he%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20one%20week%20it%20took%20to%20reach%20home%20was%20the%20worst%20week%20of%20my%20life.%20There%20was%20nobody%20willing%20to%20help%20me%20in%20the%20area%20where%20I%20lived.%20I%20survived%20thanks%20to%20the%20benevolence%20of%20kind%20strangers%20and%20other%20workers%20like%20me.%20I%20vowed%20never%20to%20go%20back%20to%20Mumbai%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumit%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20one%20who%20wished%20to%20work%20near%20his%20hometown.%20The%20nightmarish%20experience%20during%20the%20lockdown%20made%20many%20workers%20desire%20the%20same%2C%20but%20where%20were%20the%20jobs%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20country%20started%20opening%20up%20slowly%2C%20people%20had%20to%20maintain%20a%20six-foot%20distance%20in%20public%20places.%20How%20could%20100%20workers%20in%20a%20small%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowk%3C%2Fem%3E%20maintain%20distance%3F%20To%20understand%20their%20problems%20in%20detail%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20spent%20over%20four%20months%20assessing%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowks%3C%2Fem%3E%20across%20Bihar%2C%20Noida%2C%20and%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20construction%20sector%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20second-largest%20employer%20after%20agriculture.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Knight%20Frank%20%26amp%3B%20RICS%2C%2071%20million%20workers%20are%20estimated%20to%20be%20employed%20in%20this%20sector%20as%20of%202023%2C%20out%20of%20which%20over%2080%20percent%20are%20unskilled.%20When%20Chandrashekhar%20came%20across%20this%20statistic%2C%20he%20knew%20that%20there%20was%20a%20major%20gap%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20filled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20helps%20daily%20wage%20workers%20find%20jobs%20online%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk2-1722844683-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359731%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDigital%20Labour%20Chowk%20helps%20daily%20wage%20workers%20find%20jobs%20online.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20are%20platforms%20for%20finding%20white-collar%20jobs%20like%20Linkedin%2C%20Naukri%2C%20Indeed%2C%20and%20more%2C%20why%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20there%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333562%2Fassam-daily-wager-diganta-das-launches-paratha-startup-inspiring-entrepreneur-in-food-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20for%20blue-collar%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20I%20decided%20to%20build%20one%20and%20move%20the%20physical%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowks%3C%2Fem%3E%20digital.%20Daily%20wage%20workers%20too%20should%20be%20able%20to%20look%20for%20jobs%20from%20the%20comfort%20of%20their%20homes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConvinced%20about%20his%20idea%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%20in%20September%202020%20with%20Rs%2020%2C000%20in%20his%20pocket.%20Having%20already%20quit%20CA%20preparation%20after%20finishing%20the%20Inter%20exams%2C%20his%20family%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20very%20happy.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20runs%20a%20small%20shop%20and%20sent%20me%20to%20Delhi%20for%20schooling.%20He%20wanted%20me%20to%20study%20well%20and%20find%20a%20good%20job.%20When%20I%20quit%20and%20returned%20home%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20explaining%20that%20I%20had%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20chuckles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20few%20months%20were%20difficult%20as%20he%20remembers%20%E2%80%9Clooking%20at%20the%20fan%E2%80%9D%20and%20surviving%20on%20the%20savings%20he%20had!%20Chandrashekhar%20then%20started%20looking%20for%20government%20schemes%20and%20loans%20that%20he%20could%20apply%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20registering%20%E2%80%98Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20Private%20Limited%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20found%20his%20first%20investor%20in%20an%20incubator%20in%20Pune.%20The%20startup%20received%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20August%202021%2C%20kicking%20off%20a%20series%20of%20grants%20and%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20building%20the%20website%20and%20application%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20legal%20and%20technical%20aspects%2C%20the%20founder%20had%20a%20big%20task%20in%20hand%3A%20getting%20customers%20and%20workers%20to%20sign%20up.%20After%20hiring%20seven%20members%20for%20his%20team%2C%20the%20next%20challenge%20was%20wooing%20the%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20for%20blue-collar%20workers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20most%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowks%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20a%20mobile%20shop%20or%20small%20grocery%20store%20nearby%2C%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20signed%20up%20these%20shop%20owners%20