0Rs%201%20lakh.%20With%20this%20prize%20money%2C%20they%20started%20working%20on%20the%20first%20prototype%20of%20their%20cultivator%2C%20the%20Half%20Inch%20Garden.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20garden%20that%20fits%20perfectly%20on%20your%20dining%20table%20or%20coffee%20table%E2%80%9D%2C%20says%20Sayak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20received%20over%20Rs%2018%20lakh%20in%20grants%20from%20various%20institutions%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20Massive%20Earth%20Foundation%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Environment%20Programme%20(UNEP)%2C%20IIT%20Roorkee%2C%20IIM%20Kashipur%2C%20and%20more.%20The%20startup%20is%20also%20recognised%20by%20the%20Department%20for%20Promotion%20of%20Industry%20and%20Internal%20Trade%20(DPIIT)%2C%20a%20central%20government%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20automated%2C%20handy%20cultivator%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F257325%2Fhow-to-grow-microgreens-fenugreek-mustard-recycle-milk-packets-workshops-organic-farming-vegetables-nutrition-sustainable-jaipur-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoilless%20unit%20and%20comes%20with%20seed%20patches.%3C%2Fa%3E%20These%20patches%20are%20thin%20sheets%20that%20come%20embedded%20with%20seeds.%20The%20sheets%20are%20made%20using%20biodegradable%20fibres%20and%20agricultural%20waste%20like%20banana%20fibre.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sheet%20itself%20acts%20as%20a%20growing%20medium%20for%20the%20microgreens%2C%20providing%20essential%20nutrients.%20There%20are%20no%20pesticides%20required.%20We%20have%20formulated%20and%20manufactured%20this%20sheet%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sayak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20uses%20a%20hydroponic%20technology%20and%20comes%20with%20a%20grow%20light%20that%20mimics%20the%20wavelength%20of%20the%20sun.%20It%20also%20has%20two%20exhaust%20fans%20inside%20to%20circulate%20the%20airflow%20and%20an%20automatic%20irrigation%20system.%3C%2Fp